00:41:11,596 --> 00:41:14,966
Tu ne me déshonoreras pas !

761
00:41:14,966 --> 00:41:17,034
Non !

762
00:41:35,222 --> 00:41:36,759
Ryan...

763
00:41:37,483 --> 00:41:40,056
Va chercher le fourgon.

